I... I don't understand what you mean.

00:03:08.390 --> 00:03:09.460
Cranio-cerebral Injury

00:03:09.700 --> 00:03:10.540
can lead to

00:03:10.990 --> 00:03:12.580
developmental regression.

00:03:12.860 --> 00:03:14.550
As for the severity of the symptoms,

00:03:16.180 --> 00:03:17.230
we need to wait and see.

00:03:21.420 --> 00:03:22.300
Doctor.

00:03:23.140 --> 00:03:24.740
Can she be cured?

00:03:31.270 --> 00:03:32.270
It will take time.

00:03:33.830 --> 00:03:35.020
Mom.

00:03:40.070 --> 00:03:40.950
It's okay.

00:03:49.860 --> 00:03:54.420
=Persona=
=Episode 9=

00:03:56.510 --> 00:03:58.020
That day, as soon as I got home,

00:03:58.670 --> 00:04:00.620
I saw sleeping pills
scattered on the floor.

00:04:05.140 --> 00:04:07.620
I never thought I'd been living in a fog

00:04:09.020 --> 00:04:10.550
and end up hurting Mengmeng.

00:04:17.910 --> 00:04:18.820
Don't think that way.

00:04:20.470 --> 00:04:21.860
Mengmeng wouldn't either.

00:04:23.820 --> 00:04:25.380
She only wants you to be okay.

00:04:27.500 --> 00:04:29.940
You didn't see her then.

00:04:30.710 --> 00:04:32.230
I was so scared.

00:04:33.030 --> 00:04:34.620
If she stays like this forever,

00:04:34.620 --> 00:04:35.670
what will we do?

00:04:41.350 --> 00:04:43.150
I'm wondering if she's in pain.

00:04:44.820 --> 00:04:46.230
She's so little right now.

00:04:46.380 --> 00:04:48.620
Will it hurt more as she grows up?

00:04:49.820 --> 00:04:51.150
I even thought

00:04:51.910 --> 00:04:53.990
maybe we should just
end it all together.

00:04:54.180 --> 00:04:55.500
If we both died,

00:04:56.420 --> 00:04:58.590
maybe we'd both be free
from this suffering.

00:05:03.300 --> 00:05:04.620
But when I look at her

00:05:07.050 --> 00:05:08.860
(Fear's okay)
trying so hard to call me "mom",

00:05:10.030 --> 00:05:11.180
and she smiles at me

00:05:12.820 --> 00:05:14.260
to cheer me up.

00:05:16.350 --> 00:05:18.230
Then another voice appeared in my mind.

00:05:19.060 --> 00:05:19.900
I think

00:05:21.990 --> 00:05:23.620
maybe she can be cured.

00:05:27.790 --> 00:05:29.420
What if she gets cured.

00:05:35.420 --> 00:05:36.350
So I think

00:05:37.300 --> 00:05:38.420
don't leave.

00:05:40.350 --> 00:05:41.300
Just stay.

00:05:43.150 --> 00:05:44.060
At least...

00:05:44.060 --> 00:05:46.620
At least Ma Weicheng
can still pay for Mengmeng's treatment.

00:05:51.230 --> 00:05:52.860
It doesn't matter if he controls me.

00:05:55.620 --> 00:05:57.420
For Mengmeng, I can do anything.

00:06:04.420 --> 00:06:06.350
I just tell myself not to
think about it.

00:06:07.670 --> 00:06:09.230
Just live a bit more numb.

00:06:14.060 --> 00:06:16.820
Anyway, time will pass quickly.

00:06:22.060 --> 00:06:23.500
Mr. Carnegie once said,

00:06:23.990 --> 00:06:27.820
if you want both happiness and success,

00:06:27.820 --> 00:06:30.710
you must find joy in your work.

00:06:31.260 --> 00:06:32.260
Zhang Yan

00:06:32.790 --> 00:06:35.180
has found joy in her work.

00:06:35.180 --> 00:06:37.500
She is the best example of this.

00:06:38.860 --> 00:06:41.740
That's why she has achieved so much.

00:06:41.740 --> 00:06:45.340
(Gold Sales Champion)

00:06:45.350 --> 00:06:46.940
Let's give her a round of applause.

00:07:18.670 --> 00:07:20.790
Miss, could you help me find Ma?

00:07:20.790 --> 00:07:22.110
I have something urgent.

00:07:22.380 --> 00:07:23.910
Aunt, Mr. Ma is not here.

00:07:23.910 --> 00:07:25.470
Maybe come back another day.

00:07:26.150 --> 00:07:28.260
- Or could you call him?
- Godmother.

00:07:28.260 --> 00:07:29.420
Why are you here?

00:07:29.590 --> 00:07:30.430
Kid.

00:07:30.550 --> 00:07:32.030
Hurry and help me find Ma.

00:07:32.030 --> 00:07:33.230
It's urgent.

00:07:33.230 --> 00:07:34.110
I called him,

00:07:34.110 --> 00:07:35.470
but he wouldn't pick up.

00:07:35.470 --> 00:07:36.740
Relax, what happened?

00:07:36.740 --> 00:07:38.230
What's wrong?

00:07:38.790 --> 00:07:40.150
My husband fell in the bathroom

00:07:40.150 --> 00:07:41.740
this morning.

00:07:41.740 --> 00:07:43.740
And he broke his femoral head.

00:07:43.740 --> 00:07:46.060
The doctor said
he needs surgery right away.

00:07:46.060 --> 00:07:46.990
But my money...

00:07:47.150 --> 00:07:49.060
I invested it all into your shop.

00:07:49.060 --> 00:07:49.940
I need to withdraw it.

00:07:49.940 --> 00:07:51.500
I need my money back.

00:07:51.740 --> 00:07:53.110
What investment?

00:07:53.380 --> 00:07:55.300
When did our store ask for investments?

00:07:56.230 --> 00:07:58.420
You... you didn't know?

00:07:58.620 --> 00:08:00.550
Ma approached me privately.

00:08:00.780 --> 00:08:02.230
He said about the new branch.

00:08:02.230 --> 00:08:04.030
Since I've spent so much
on membership cards

00:08:04.030 --> 00:08:05.620
and I'm a long-time customer,

00:08:05.620 --> 00:08:07.260
he asked
if I wanted to be a shareholder.

00:08:07.260 --> 00:08:08.500
He said shareholders can

00:08:08.500 --> 00:08:09.910
get discounts on products.

00:08:09.910 --> 00:08:11.420
And I could also receive dividends.

00:08:11.420 --> 00:08:13.470
Ma gave me dividends for two months.

00:08:13.470 --> 00:08:15.790
But now,
but now my husband is in trouble.

00:08:16.110 --> 00:08:17.380
I need to use money.

00:08:17.380 --> 00:08:18.230
I have to hurry...

00:08:18.230 --> 00:08:20.380
Kid, help me figure this out.

00:08:20.710 --> 00:08:22.260
I can only count on you.

00:08:23.320 --> 00:08:24.180
Okay.

00:08:24.300 --> 00:08:25.180
Then I'll go ask.

00:08:25.180 --> 00:08:26.740
- Wait for me.
- Alright, alright.

00:08:26.940 --> 00:08:28.230
I'll wait for your news.

00:08:33.740 --> 00:08:34.580
Come in.

00:08:34.820 --> 00:08:38.300
(Welcome to Jiankanglu)

00:08:43.070 --> 00:08:43.910
Mr. Ma.

00:08:44.500 --> 00:08:45.590
Ms. Li is here.

00:08:46.140 --> 00:08:48.470
She said her husband needs surgery
and requires money.

00:08:49.590 --> 00:08:51.500
She had invested in our business before.

00:08:51.500 --> 00:08:52.860
It was handled by you.

00:08:53.430 --> 00:08:55.230
She's asking
if she can get her money back.

00:08:59.350 --> 00:09:01.020
You really think
you're her real daughter?

00:09:04.660 --> 00:09:06.070
Mengmeng's condition means

00:09:07.190 --> 00:09:08.990
we'll need more money later.

00:09:10.350 --> 00:09:12.070
Who has time for other people's affairs?

00:09:14.110 --> 00:09:15.140
Just say something

00:09:15.140 --> 00:09:16.540
to send her away.

00:09:16.540 --> 00:09:17.380
Mr. Ma.

00:09:20.950 --> 00:09:21.790
Go ahead.

00:09:22.070 --> 00:09:22.990
You can do it.

00:09:35.500 --> 00:09:36.740
Kid, how is it going?

00:09:36.740 --> 00:09:38.950
Godmother,
maybe you should go home for today.

00:09:38.950 --> 00:09:40.110
I'll think of another way.

00:09:40.430 --> 00:09:41.310
What's wrong?

00:09:41.660 --> 00:09:42.990
Ma refused, didn't he?

00:09:42.990 --> 00:09:44.780
Tell me, is he inside?

00:09:44.780 --> 00:09:45.900
No, I'll go find him myself.

00:09:45.900 --> 00:09:47.590
- That's my own money.
- Godmother.

00:09:47.590 --> 00:09:48.950
I must get that money back!

00:09:48.950 --> 00:09:50.020
Ms. Li.

00:09:52.380 --> 00:09:53.220
Come here.

00:10:05.990 --> 00:10:06.830
Ms. Li.

00:10:07.260 --> 00:10:08.900
The money you invested

00:10:09.260 --> 00:10:10.950
cannot be returned.

00:10:11.950 --> 00:10:13.710
I was very clear with you
from the start.

00:10:13.710 --> 00:10:14.660
This money

00:10:14.660 --> 00:10:16.740
was for our new branch in Zhangzhou.

00:10:16.740 --> 00:10:18.660
The branch is already open.

00:10:18.660 --> 00:10:19.990
How can we return the money?

00:10:19.990 --> 00:10:23.140
Wait,
I don't want the dividends anymore.

00:10:23.260 --> 00:10:26.430
Ma, just return my principal to me.

00:10:26.740 --> 00:10:28.540
I don't need the full amount.

00:10:28.540 --> 00:10:30.190
Keep whatever you've spent.

00:10:30.500 --> 00:10:33.260
Just give me back
a couple hundred thousand, please.

00:10:33.260 --> 00:10:34.430
Ms. Li, Ms. Li.

00:10:34.780 --> 00:10:36.230
How about you think it over again?

00:10:36.430 --> 00:10:37.860
After all, this investment

00:10:37.860 --> 00:10:39.710
gives you thousands
in dividends each month.

00:10:39.710 --> 00:10:41.230
Where else get a deal this good?

00:10:41.780 --> 00:10:43.190
If I had another way,

00:10:43.190 --> 00:10:44.430
I wouldn't be here.

00:10:44.430 --> 00:10:45.900
- Wait, don't do this.
- Get up first.

00:10:45.900 --> 00:10:47.260
I treated you all like family.

00:10:47.260 --> 00:10:48.350
- Please!
- We can't take this.

00:10:48.350 --> 00:10:50.190
- Get up first.
- Save my husband, okay?

00:10:50.190 --> 00:10:51.230
Get up first, get up.

00:10:51.740 --> 00:10:54.190
No, if you don't agree, I won't get up.

00:10:55.990 --> 00:10:57.310
Alright, I promise you.

00:10:57.310 --> 00:10:59.710
Come on, get up now.

00:10:59.710 --> 00:11:00.580
Then...

00:11:00.620 --> 00:11:01.460
Ms. Li.

00:11:02.140 --> 00:11:03.780
If this company were mine,

00:11:04.190 --> 00:11:05.540
I'd give you the money right now.

00:11:05.830 --> 00:11:07.760
- So...
- But I am just an agent.

00:11:11.350 --> 00:11:12.190
How about this.

00:11:13.190 --> 00:11:14.350
Give me some time.

00:11:15.070 --> 00:11:16.230
Trust me.

00:11:16.230 --> 00:11:17.660
I'll call headquarters.

00:11:17.660 --> 00:11:19.470
See if there's a special procedure

00:11:19.470 --> 00:11:20.430
we can apply for.

00:11:20.740 --> 00:11:22.620
Then we return your shares to you, okay?

00:11:22.620 --> 00:11:25.070
Alright, then my spouse can be saved.

00:11:25.070 --> 00:11:26.470
But, but...

00:11:26.470 --> 00:11:27.780
Headquarters is overseas.

00:11:27.780 --> 00:11:29.070
There's a time difference.

00:11:29.070 --> 00:11:29.930
Once they start work,

00:11:29.940 --> 00:11:31.380
I will give them a call.

00:11:31.380 --> 00:11:32.220
Alright?

00:11:32.750 --> 00:11:33.900
Go back and take care of uncle.

00:11:33.900 --> 00:11:35.070
Don't overthink.

00:11:35.070 --> 00:11:35.910
Here, Manager Zhang.

00:11:35.920 --> 00:11:36.900
See Aunt out.

00:11:38.070 --> 00:11:39.110
Alright.

00:11:39.110 --> 00:11:41.260
Ma, I'll wait for your news.

00:11:42.830 --> 00:11:44.830
Ma, let me know as soon as
you have news.

00:11:44.830 --> 00:11:45.780
Okay.

00:12:09.350 --> 00:12:10.190
Have you eaten?

00:12:10.190 --> 00:12:11.660
Yes, you go ahead.

00:12:11.780 --> 00:12:12.620
Alright.

00:12:48.190 --> 00:12:49.030
What's wrong?

00:12:49.620 --> 00:12:50.500
Need money?

00:12:53.590 --> 00:12:54.590
For Mengmeng's recovery,

00:12:55.020 --> 00:12:56.070
the hospital needs payment.

00:13:00.350 --> 00:13:01.430
Don't use that card.

00:13:01.860 --> 00:13:02.830
That card has no money.

00:13:05.310 --> 00:13:06.780
What does the hospital need money for?

00:13:07.350 --> 00:13:09.230
You can ask them to contact me directly.

00:13:11.830 --> 00:13:13.860
You've already spent so much
on Mengmeng.

00:13:14.430 --> 00:13:16.140
From now on,
let's manage our own expenses.

00:13:16.140 --> 00:13:17.500
Give me my money.

00:13:22.500 --> 00:13:23.500
Your money.

00:13:24.860 --> 00:13:26.190
You don't have any money left.

00:13:29.740 --> 00:13:31.140
Don't think I don't know.

00:13:32.860 --> 00:13:33.700
You...

00:13:34.230 --> 00:13:36.020
just want to use my money

00:13:36.020 --> 00:13:37.780
to pay back your so-called godmother.

00:13:38.430 --> 00:13:40.070
You never intended to refund her.

00:13:40.250 --> 00:13:41.740
That's her spouse's life-saving money.

00:13:41.740 --> 00:13:43.020
How can you be so cruel?

00:13:43.230 --> 00:13:44.860
We don't have the Zhangzhou store.

00:13:45.020 --> 00:13:46.710
You kept all that money for yourself.

00:13:46.710 --> 00:13:48.140
You need to understand

00:13:49.590 --> 00:13:51.310
who is really on your side.

00:13:53.430 --> 00:13:54.270
Is it your dad?

00:13:54.540 --> 00:13:55.380
Your mom?

00:13:56.470 --> 00:13:57.780
Or that ex-husband?

00:14:02.190 --> 00:14:04.020
Did any of them care
if you lived or died?

00:14:05.620 --> 00:14:08.070
Now you're taking my money for them.

00:14:08.660 --> 00:14:10.540
How can you be so shameless?

00:14:15.540 --> 00:14:18.310
You'd better
keep your mouth shut about this.

00:14:19.230 --> 00:14:20.470
What if one day

00:14:20.470 --> 00:14:21.430
Mengmeng gets in trouble

00:14:21.430 --> 00:14:22.320
and we need money.

00:14:22.330 --> 00:14:23.780
What will we do?

00:16:33.140 --> 00:16:34.690
(Kid, when will I get my refund?)

00:16:34.690 --> 00:16:36.540
(The hospital is urging me again)

00:16:36.540 --> 00:16:37.780
(I went to your store)

00:16:37.780 --> 00:16:39.780
(You weren't there, and neither was Ma.)

00:16:39.780 --> 00:16:42.260
(Are you guys lying to me)

00:17:02.060 --> 00:17:02.990
Did you see that?

00:17:02.990 --> 00:17:03.830
She's back at work.

00:17:04.100 --> 00:17:05.500
I thought she had resigned.

00:17:05.870 --> 00:17:07.990
Probably thinks
the old lady's problem is over.

00:17:07.990 --> 00:17:08.870
So she came.

00:17:09.670 --> 00:17:11.740
What happened to that old lady?

00:17:11.740 --> 00:17:12.670
I don't know.

00:17:12.990 --> 00:17:14.430
Those days she came making a scene.

00:17:14.430 --> 00:17:15.630
No one dared to deal with her.

00:17:15.870 --> 00:17:17.100
Better not to ask too much.

00:17:40.020 --> 00:17:41.060
You're Zhang Yan, right?

00:17:44.140 --> 00:17:45.150
(Police)
There is a case.

00:17:45.150 --> 00:17:46.390
Please come with us

00:17:46.390 --> 00:17:47.260
for the investigation.

00:17:59.580 --> 00:18:01.100
Li Bingmei was your client, right?

00:18:03.340 --> 00:18:04.260
Yes.

00:18:05.060 --> 00:18:07.820
She bought some health products
at our store.

00:18:08.190 --> 00:18:09.580
I was the one who served her.

00:18:11.340 --> 00:18:12.390
Did you know your store

00:18:12.390 --> 00:18:13.780
planned to open a new branch?

00:18:21.430 --> 00:18:23.910
Did you know Ma Weicheng
tricked customers into investing

00:18:23.910 --> 00:18:25.500
in the name of opening a new store?

00:18:33.100 --> 00:18:34.230
Just say whatever you know.

00:18:34.470 --> 00:18:35.580
Don't hold back.

00:18:42.820 --> 00:18:44.470
Li Bingmei invested 200,000 yuan.

00:18:46.630 --> 00:18:47.670
This is her mobile phone.

00:18:48.190 --> 00:18:49.340
Her last text message

00:18:49.340 --> 00:18:50.500
and phone call

00:18:50.500 --> 00:18:51.780
were both to you.

00:18:52.500 --> 00:18:53.820
Since we called you over,

00:18:53.820 --> 00:18:55.100
it means we already have

00:18:55.100 --> 00:18:55.990
certain leads.

00:18:59.820 --> 00:19:01.190
Did Ms. Li call the police?

00:19:07.190 --> 00:19:08.230
She jumped off a building.

00:19:13.670 --> 00:19:15.630
Now you understand how serious this is?

00:19:19.340 --> 00:19:21.020
How is Aunt Li now?

00:19:21.760 --> 00:19:23.020
Still in hospital, critical care.

00:19:23.500 --> 00:19:25.190
We don't know if she'll wake up.

00:19:30.690 --> 00:19:32.430
I didn't expect
it would turn out like this.

00:19:32.430 --> 00:19:33.270
Officer.

00:19:34.740 --> 00:19:36.470
I really didn't expect this.

00:19:36.630 --> 00:19:38.230
When her son reported it,

00:19:38.330 --> 00:19:40.430
he said his dad passed away
before getting surgery.

00:19:40.820 --> 00:19:42.540
All because the money was stolen.

00:19:42.710 --> 00:19:44.470
His mom couldn't live with the guilt.

00:19:45.100 --> 00:19:46.630
Right after his dad's funeral,

00:19:46.870 --> 00:19:48.260
she jumped.

00:19:54.580 --> 00:19:55.420
Zhang Yan.

00:19:56.990 --> 00:19:57.990
What's done is done.

00:19:58.710 --> 00:20:01.670
Feeling sad or guilty won't help.

00:20:02.910 --> 00:20:05.020
Because the amount
involved in this case is large

00:20:05.340 --> 00:20:06.950
and the victim was seriously injured,

00:20:07.060 --> 00:20:08.630
the circumstances are extremely bad.

00:20:09.100 --> 00:20:10.340
The only thing you can do now

00:20:10.340 --> 00:20:11.820
is to assist the police.

00:20:12.540 --> 00:20:13.950
To bring the criminal to justice.

00:20:14.190 --> 00:20:15.780
And give the victim justice.

00:20:16.020 --> 00:20:16.860
Do you understand?

00:20:50.300 --> 00:20:51.260
Ma Weicheng, right?

00:20:54.900 --> 00:20:55.950
You are suspected of fraud.

00:20:56.430 --> 00:20:57.300
Come with us.

